claim.claim-text:
5. A method for entering a word the method comprising: 
selecting one mode from a plurality of modes; 
selecting a group of letters from a plurality of groups of letters associated with that mode corresponding to a desired letter, wherein each group of letters includes a plurality of letters; 
repeating the mode selection and the group selection until all of the groups that contain all of letters of a desired word have been selected; and 
determining the desire word using a word recognition means.
